description: Welcome to 265 C Street, enjoy 817 sqft of modern living in this expansive 1-bedroom home. The open floor plan features an updated kitchen, a newly renovated bathroom, and the convenience of an in-unit washer and dryer. Sunlight fills this corner unit, highlighting its generous layout and abundant closet space. Stay comfortable year-round with efficient ductless heating and cooling.Step outside to your private, gated patio—perfect for entertaining—which leads directly to your deeded end-unit parking space. With two private entrances, this home offers a townhouse-style feel. Additional perks include a massive private storage unit and easy access to the building’s amenities.  Located just a short walk to the Broadway T Stop, West Broadway shops, and top-rated restaurants, this home offers unbeatable convenience in a prime city location!
